reduceCtorParamRefl2/name : name "reduceCtorParamRefl2" (is-decl (eforall (esort (lsucc lzero)) ([x] (esort (lsucc lzero)))) (indt (ccons "reduceCtorParamRefl2.mk" cnil) (s z))).

